Hardware Requirements
• Raspberry Pi (Model 3B+, 4, or Zero W)
• Breadboard
• 4 to 6 tactile push-buttons
• Jumper wires (male-to-male and male-to-female)
• Resistors (optional for pull-down configuration)
• Speaker or headphone output
• MicroSD card with Raspberry Pi OS
• 5V power supply for Raspberry Pi
Software Requirements
• Raspberry Pi OS (Bullseye or later)
• Python 3
• Libraries: gpiozero, pygame
• Preloaded sound samples in .wav or .flac format
Installation command:
sudo apt update
sudo apt install python3-gpiozero python3-pygame
